            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc185328695_anchor">Comprehensive Module: Guidance</a></span>
            
          </div>
          <div class="TOC2_NoBottomMargin" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; align-items:baseline; margin-left:15px">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc185328696_anchor">Comprehensive Module Guidance – General information</a></span>
            
          </div>
          <div class="TOC2_noTopMargin_NoBottomMargin" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; align-items:baseline; margin-left:15px">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc185328697_anchor">Comprehensive Module Guidance – Environmental Metrics</a></span>
            
          </div>
          <div class="TOC2_noTopMargin_NoBottomMargin" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; align-items:baseline; margin-left:15px">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc185328698_anchor">Comprehensive Module Guidance – Social Metrics</a></span>
            
          </div>
          <div class="TOC2_noTopMargin" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; align-items:baseline; margin-left:15px">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc185328699_anchor">Comprehensive Module Guidance – Business Conduct Metrics</a></span>
            
          </div>
          <div class="TOC1_NoBottomMargin" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; align-items:baseline; margin-right:32px">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc185328700_anchor">Appendix A: Defined terms</a></span>
            
          </div>
          <div class="TOC1_noTopMargin_NoBottomMargin" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; align-items:baseline; margin-right:32px">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc145948480_anchor">Appendix B: List of possible sustainability issues</a></span>
            
          </div>
          <div class="TOC1_noTopMargin" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; align-items:baseline; margin-right:32px">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr"><a href="#BM__Toc185328702_anchor">Appendix
 C: Background information for financial market participants that are 
users of the information produced using this Standard (reconciliation 
with other EU regulations)</a></span>
            
          </div>
				</div>
				<div class="page_footer_after_0">
					<div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="font-style:italic; margin-top:0px"></div>

