        <div class="page_body_after_0">
          <div class="BasicnumberredN_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight">Pictograms
 that indicate hazardous properties, Annex V, from the Classification, 
Labelling and Packaging (CLP) Regulation (EC) No 1272/2008.</div>
          <div class="BasicnumberredN_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
            <span class="numbering-583-level-0" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal" dir="ltr" id="id-348">
              <a href="#id-348">168.</a>
            </span>
            <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">When presenting 
information on its waste generation or diversion from disposal, the 
undertaking should preferably report such information in units of weight
 (e.g. kg or tonnes). Nevertheless, should the units of weight be 
considered an inappropriate unit by the undertaking, they may 
alternatively disclose the aforementioned metrics in volumes (e.g. m3) 
instead.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="BasicnumberredN_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
            <span class="numbering-583-level-0" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal" dir="ltr" id="id-349">
              <a href="#id-349">169.</a>
            </span>
            <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">When disclosing information on the total annual waste diverted to</span>
            <span style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; display:contents" dir="ltr">recycling</span>
            <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">or reuse, the 
undertaking should consider the waste that is sorted and sent to 
recycling or reuse operators (e.g. the amount of waste put into 
recycling container or sorting of waste into certain categories of 
materials and their delivery to waste treatment facilities) rather than 
the waste that gets effectively recycled or reused.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="BasicnumberredN_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
            <span class="numbering-583-level-0" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal" dir="ltr" id="id-350">
              <a href="#id-350">170.</a>
            </span>
            <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">When disclosing information on waste, the undertaking may adopt the following tables.</span>
