              </td>
              <td class="d2d1718">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-align:right; margin-top:0px"> </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <div class="Footer" style="text-align:justify"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page_after_0">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="page_header_after_0">
          <div class="Header-nextpage">VSME Standard</div>
        </div>
        <div class="page_body_after_0">
          <div class="Header1">
            <span id="BM__Toc185328701_anchor" class="hyperlink-no-style"></span>
            <span id="BM__Toc145948480_anchor" class="hyperlink-no-style"></span>
            <span style="font-size:16px; min-height:16px" dir="ltr">Appendix B: List of possible sustainability issues</span>
          </div>
          <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="page-break-after:avoid">
            <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr">The appendix below is an integral part of this Standard and provides a list of possible sustainability issues.</span>
          </div>
          <table class="TableNormal" style="width:604px; background-color:#FFFFFF; border-collapse:collapse; margin:0px auto 0px 0px; border:0.2pt solid #000000; border-style:single" dir="ltr">
            <tr>
              <td colspan="3" class="a2d605">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="font-size:13px; font-weight:bold; min-height:13px; margin:7px 0px"></div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="d23983">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px">
                  <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px; font-weight:bold" dir="ltr">Topic</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d01a9e">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px">
                  <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px; font-weight:bold" dir="ltr">Sustainability issue: Sub-topic</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d5709b7">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px">
                  <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px; font-weight:bold" dir="ltr">Sustainability issue: sub-sub topic</span>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="d3cbd32">
              <td class="f9d38b">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px">
                  <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr">Climate change</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d8820f0">
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-436">
                    <a href="#id-436"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Climate change adaptation</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-437">
                    <a href="#id-437"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Climate change mitigation</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-438">
                    <a href="#id-438"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Energy</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d5f4b38">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px; margin:7px 0px"></div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="f9d38b">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px">
                  <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr">Pollution</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d8820f0">
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-439">
                    <a href="#id-439"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Pollution of air</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-440">
                    <a href="#id-440"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Pollution of water</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-441">
                    <a href="#id-441"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Pollution of soil</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-442">
                    <a href="#id-442"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Pollution of living organisms and food resources</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-443">
                    <a href="#id-443"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Substances of concern</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-444">
                    <a href="#id-444"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Substances of very high concern</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-445">
                    <a href="#id-445"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Microplastics</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d5f4b38">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px; margin:7px 0px"></div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="d093b37">
              <td class="f9d38b">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-align:left; margin-top:7px; margin-bottom:7px">
                  <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px" dir="ltr">Water and marine resources</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d8820f0">
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-446">
                    <a href="#id-446"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Water</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-447">
                    <a href="#id-447"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Marine resources</span>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="d5f4b38">
                <div class="ListParagraph_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:0px">
                  <span class="numbering-21-level-0" style="font-family:'Symbol'; min-height:0" dir="ltr" id="id-448">
                    <a href="#id-448"></a>
                  </span>
                  <span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">Water consumption</span>
