                <div class="BasicnumberredN_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="margin-left:24px">The undertaking shall disclose its estimated<span style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic" dir="ltr">gross greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions</span>in tons of CO<sub>2</sub>equivalent (tCO<sub>2</sub>eq) considering the content of the GHG Protocol Corporate Standard (version 2004), including:</div>
