				</div>
                <div class="BasicnumberredN_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="text-indent:0; display:flex; margin-left:38px">
                  <div>
					<span class="numbering-537-level-0" style="font-family:'Arial'; color:#000000" dir="ltr" id="id-551">
						<a href="#id-551">(b)</a>
					</span>
				</div>
				<div>
					<span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">the location-based Scope 2 emissions in tCO</span>
					<span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">
						<sub>2</sub>
					</span>
					<span style="display:contents" dir="ltr">eq (i.e. emissions from the generation of purchased energy, such as electricity, heat, steam or cooling).</span>
                </div>
				</div>
