                  </sup>
                </div>
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight" style="line-height:1.1; margin-bottom:11px">
                  <span style="font-size:13px; min-height:13px; font-weight:bold" dir="ltr">EBA Pillar 3</span>
                  <sup id="cross-fn-ref53">
                    <a href="#fn-ref53" class="hyperlink-no-style">53</a>
                  </sup>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="d9e9f74">
              <td class="d1d1268">
                <div class="BasicnumberredN_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight">The
 undertaking shall disclose whether it is excluded from any EU reference
 benchmarks that are aligned with the Paris Agreement as described in 
paragraph 241 of the guidance.</div>
              </td>
              <td class="d9cfa26">
                <div class="Normal_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight_MarginsClippedToRowHeight">
